headline: Steel Dynamics Announces Completion of Notes Offering
summary: Steel Dynamics, Inc. (NASDAQ/GS: STLD) announced today that it has consummated the sale of $600 million aggregate principal amount of 5.250% Notes due 2035 (the "2035 Notes") and $400 million aggregate principal amount of 5.750% Notes due 2055 (together with the 2035 Notes, the "Notes"). The net proceeds from the Notes will be used for general corporate purposes, which may include repayment of the company's $400 million 2.400% Senior Notes due June 2025.
